pos/python/mypy/pulls/17850","html_url":"https://github.com/python/mypy/pull/17850","diff_url":"https://github.com/python/mypy/pull/17850.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/python/mypy/pull/17850.patch","merged_at":"2024-09-30T23:35:25Z"},"body":"Fixes #15235\r\n\r\n### Before\r\n```python\r\nfrom typing import TypeVar\r\n\r\nclass A:\r\n    pass\r\nclass B:\r\n    b: int\r\n\r\nT = TypeVar(\"T\", bound=A | B)\r\n\r\n\r\ndef foo(x: T) -> T:\r\n    if isinstance(x, A):\r\n        reveal_type(x)      # N: Revealed type is \"__main__.A\"\r\n    else:\r\n        reveal_type(x)      # N: Revealed type is \"T`-1\"\r\n        x.b                 # E: Item \"A\" of the upper bound \"A | B\" of type variable \"T\" has no attribute \"b\"\r\n    return x\r\n```\r\n### After\r\n```python\r\nfrom typing import TypeVar\r\n\r\nclass A:\r\n    pass\r\nclass B:\r\n    b: int\r\n\r\nT = TypeVar(\"T\", bound=A | B)\r\n\r\n\r\ndef foo(x: T) -> T:\r\n    if isinstance(x, A):\r\n        reveal_type(x)      # N: Revealed type is \"__main__.A\"\r\n    else:\r\n        reveal_type(x)      # N: Revealed type is \"T`-1\"\r\n        x.b                 # ok! Upper bound of T narrowed to B\r\n    return x\r\n```\r\n\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/python/mypy/issues/17850/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":2,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/python/mypy/issues/17850/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":14446536124,"node_id":"LE_lADOAGuhRc5l1g_9zwAAAANdFKW8","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/python/mypy/issues/events/14446536124","actor":{"login":"AlexWaygood","id":66076021,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY2MDc2MDIx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/66076021?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/AlexWaygood","html_url":"https://github.com/AlexWaygood","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Alex